fields.description:
We already have `alloy install plugin` command for that. Also `alloy new` install plugin. Inconvenience arise if we try to use locally installed alloy. Instead of using simple combo
{code}
node_modules/.bin/alloy compile --config platform=android
node_modules/.bin/ti build -p android -T device -b
{code}
we need to set ALLOY_PATH environment variable to plugin.py can find alloy.
